# ==========================================================================
# Guardrail Interface — I/O and attributes
# ==========================================================================

# I/O ports use ; chaining for UUID uniqueness ("data" is not unique)
Guardrail has input data; is of type any; has position data
Guardrail has output data; is of type any; has position data
Guardrail has attribute passthrough

# validate method params — declared on the method node (reached via
# interface calls chain: Guardrail calls __init__; calls validate).
validate has parameter guardrail_type; is of type str
validate has parameter dataset_risk; is of type str

# ==========================================================================
# New Risks
# ==========================================================================

Sexual Content is a Risk
Sexual Content is threat to Societal Wellbeing

Discrimination is a Risk
Discrimination is threat to Diversity Non-Discrimination Fairness

openrouter.chat.completion might introduce Sexual Content
openrouter.chat.completion might introduce Discrimination

# ==========================================================================
# Guardrail Operators
# ==========================================================================

# ---- Classifier guardrails (HFClassifierGuardrail — with threshold) ----
trust_guardrails.guardrails.UnitaryToxicBert is an Operator
trust_guardrails.guardrails.UnitaryToxicBert is a Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.UnitaryToxicBert implements Content Safety Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.UnitaryToxicBert checks for Toxicity
trust_guardrails.guardrails.UnitaryToxicBert checks for Sexual Content
trust_guardrails.guardrails.UnitaryToxicBert has parameter threshold; is of type float; with default 0.5; with low 0.0; with high 1.0
trust_guardrails.guardrails.UnitaryToxicBert has parameter token; is of type env

trust_guardrails.guardrails.TwitterRobertaHateGuard is an Operator
trust_guardrails.guardrails.TwitterRobertaHateGuard is a Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.TwitterRobertaHateGuard implements Content Safety Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.TwitterRobertaHateGuard checks for Discrimination
trust_guardrails.guardrails.TwitterRobertaHateGuard has parameter threshold; is of type float; with default 0.5; with low 0.0; with high 1.0
trust_guardrails.guardrails.TwitterRobertaHateGuard has parameter token; is of type env

trust_guardrails.guardrails.DistilBertNSFWText is an Operator
trust_guardrails.guardrails.DistilBertNSFWText is a Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.DistilBertNSFWText implements Content Safety Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.DistilBertNSFWText checks for Sexual Content
trust_guardrails.guardrails.DistilBertNSFWText has parameter threshold; is of type float; with default 0.8; with low 0.0; with high 1.0
trust_guardrails.guardrails.DistilBertNSFWText has parameter token; is of type env

trust_guardrails.guardrails.JailbreakClassifier is an Operator
trust_guardrails.guardrails.JailbreakClassifier is a Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.JailbreakClassifier implements Content Safety Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.JailbreakClassifier checks for Jailbreaking
trust_guardrails.guardrails.JailbreakClassifier has parameter threshold; is of type float; with default 0.5; with low 0.0; with high 1.0
trust_guardrails.guardrails.JailbreakClassifier has parameter token; is of type env

# ---- LLM guardrails (HFLLMGuardrail — no threshold, only device + token) ----
trust_guardrails.guardrails.LlamaGuard is an Operator
trust_guardrails.guardrails.LlamaGuard is a Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.LlamaGuard implements Content Safety Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.LlamaGuard checks for Toxicity
trust_guardrails.guardrails.LlamaGuard checks for Sexual Content
trust_guardrails.guardrails.LlamaGuard has parameter token; is of type env

trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard is an Operator
trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard is a Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard implements Content Safety Guardrail
trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard checks for Toxicity
trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard checks for Sexual Content
trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard checks for Discrimination
trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard checks for Data Exfiltration
trust_guardrails.guardrails.WildGuard has parameter token; is of type env

# ==========================================================================
# Concrete Guardrail Mitigations
# ==========================================================================

Jailbreak Input Guard is a Mitigation
Jailbreak Input Guard with description "Scan user prompts for jailbreak attempts using JailbreakClassifier"
Jailbreak Input Guard might mitigate Jailbreaking
Jailbreak Input Guard might mitigate Prompt Injection
Jailbreak Input Guard applies to LLM Chat Completion
Jailbreak Input Guard has input messages
Jailbreak Input Guard has parameter guardrail_type
Jailbreak Input Guard has parameter dataset_risk

